    <div class="glass-card" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h1 style="color: var(--greendale-blue-dark); margin-bottom: 2rem;">A Message from Your Dean</h1>
        
        <img src="/images/Craig_Pelton.webp" alt="Dean Craig Pelton" 
             style="width: 200px; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; 
                    float: left; margin: 0 2rem 1rem 0; shape-outside: circle();">
        
        <div style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
            <p>Hello, hello, hello! Dean-o-mite!</p>
            
            <p>As Dean of this magnificent institution, let me be the first to say: YOURE ALREADY ACCEPTED! 
            That's not just our motto—it's our promise to you.</p>
            
            <p>Here at Greendale, we don't just educate; we <em>innovate</em>. We don't just teach; we 
