            interpretive dance troupe, or your secret trampoline society (shh, don't tell the insurance company).</p>
            
            <p>Remember: at Greendale, failure is just success rounded down. So click that login button, 
            and let's make some educational magic happen!</p>
            
            <p style="text-align: right; font-style: italic; color: var(--greendale-blue);">
                —Dean Craig Pelton
            </p>
